                            <label class="day-checkbox-item">

                                <input type="checkbox" id="dayThursday" value="4" checked>

                                <span>חמישי</span>

                            </label>

                            <label class="day-checkbox-item">

                                <input type="checkbox" id="dayFriday" value="5" checked>

                                <span>שישי</span>

                            </label>

                            <label class="day-checkbox-item">

                                <input type="checkbox" id="daySaturday" value="6" checked>

                                <span>שבת</span>

                            </label>

                        </div>

                        <small class="form-help">

                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>

                            בחר באילו ימים בשבוע המשימה תופיע

                        </small>

                    </div>

 

                    <!-- History will be inserted here by JavaScript -->

                </div>

 

                <!-- Fixed footer with buttons -->

                <div class="modal-footer">

                    <div class="form-actions">

                        <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="dailyTasksManager.closeAddTaskModal()">ביטול</button>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary" id="taskSubmitBtn">הוסף משימה</button>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </form>

        </div>

    </div>

 

    <!-- Skip Reason Modal -->

    <div id="skipReasonModal" class="skip-reason-modal">

        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">

                <h2 class="modal-title">סיבת אי ביצוע משימה</h2>

                <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeSkipReasonModal()">&times;</button>

            </div>

 

            <form id="skipReasonForm">

                <input type="hidden" id="skipTaskId" value="">

 

                <div class="form-group">

                    <label class="form-label">משימה:</label>

                    <div id="skipTaskTitle" class="task-title-display"></div>

                </div>

 

                <div class="form-group">

                    <label class="form-label">שם העובד *</label>

                    <select id="skipUserName" class="form-select" required>

                        <option value="">בחר עובד...</option>

                    </select>

                </div>

 

                <div class="form-group">

                    <label class="form-label">סיבת אי ביצוע *</label>

                    <select id="skipReasonSelect" class="form-select" onchange="handleSkipReasonChange()">

                        <option value="">בחר סיבה...</option>

                        <option value="חוסר זמן">חוסר זמן</option>

                        <option value="בעיה טכנית">בעיה טכנית</option>

                        <option value="חוסר גישה למערכת">חוסר גישה למערכת</option>

                        <option value="משימה לא רלוונטית">משימה לא רלוונטית</option>

                        <option value="ממתין לאישור">ממתין לאישור</option>

                        <option value="תלוי במשימה אחרת">תלוי במשימה אחרת</option>

                        <option value="אחר">אחר...</option>

                    </select>

                </div>

 

                <div class="form-group" id="customReasonGroup" style="display: none;">

                    <label class="form-label">פרט את הסיבה:</label>

                    <textarea id="skipReasonCustom" class="form-textarea" rows="3"

                        placeholder="הזן סיבה מותאמת אישית..."></textarea>

                </div>

 

                <div class="form-actions">

                    <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="closeSkipReasonModal()">ביטול</button>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn-warning">סמן כלא בוצע</button>

                </div>

            </form>

        </div>

    </div>

 

    <!-- Add/Edit Employee Task Modal -->

    <div id="addEmployeeTaskModal" class="add-employee-task-modal">

        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">

                <h2 id="employeeTaskModalTitle" class="modal-title">הוסף משימה לעובד</h2>

                <button type="button" class="close-btn" onclick="closeAddEmployeeTaskModal()">

                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                </button>

            </div>

           

            <!-- Scrollable Body -->

            <div class="modal-body">

                <form id="addEmployeeTaskForm">

                    <input type="hidden" id="employeeTaskId" name="taskId">

                    <input type="hidden" id="assignedEmployeeId" name="employeeId">

                    <input type="hidden" id="employeeTaskAssignDate" name="taskDate">

                    

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label">עובד נבחר</label>

                        <select id="selectedEmployeeSelect" class="form-select" required>

                            <option value="">בחר עובד...</option>

                        </select>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label">כותרת המשימה *</label>

                        <input type="text" id="employeeTaskTitle" class="form-input" required>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label">תיאור המשימה</label>

                        <textarea id="employeeTaskDescription" class="form-textarea"></textarea>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label">עדיפות</label>

                        <select id="employeeTaskPriority" class="form-select">

                            <option value="low">נמוכה</option>

                            <option value="medium" selected>בינונית</option>

                            <option value="high">גבוהה</option>

                        </select>

                    </div>

 

                   <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label">תאריך לסיום ביצוע (אופציונלי)</label>

                        <div class="date-input-wrapper">

                            <input type="date" id="employeeTaskDueDateHidden" class="hidden-date-input"

                                onchange="handleDueDateChange(this.value)">

                            <input type="text" id="employeeTaskDueDate" placeholder="DD/MM/YYYY" readonly

                                onclick="openDueDatePicker()" class="formatted-date-input">

                            <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt date-icon" onclick="openDueDatePicker()"></i>

                            <button type="button" id="employeeTaskDueDateClear" class="time-clear-btn" onclick="employeeTasksManager.clearDueDate()" style="display: none;" title="נקה שדה תאריך יעד">

                                <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                            </button>

                        </div>

                        <small class="form-help">בחר תאריך יעד לסיום המשימה</small>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label">זמן עבודה משוער (אופציונלי)</label>

                        <input type="text" id="employeeTaskTime" class="form-input" placeholder="לדוגמה: 30 דקות">

                    </div>

                </form>

            </div>

            <div class="modal-footer">

                <div class="form-actions">

                    <button type="button" id="employeeTaskSubmitBtn" class="btn-primary" onclick="handleEmployeeTaskSubmit(event)">

                        הוסף משימה

                    </button>

                    <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="closeAddEmployeeTaskModal()">

                        ביטול

                    </button>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

 

    <!-- Employee Selection Modal - Job completed in messages-->

    <div id="employeeSelectionModal" class="employee-job-completed-modal">

        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">

                <h3 class="modal-title">

                    <i class="fas fa-user-check"></i>

                    סימון משימה כהושלמה

                </h3>

                <button class="close-btn" onclick="messagesManager.closeEmployeeSelectionModal()">

                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                </button>

            </div>

            <form id="employeeSelectionForm" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();

                const messageId = document.getElementById('completionMessageId').value;

                const jobIndex = document.getElementById('completionJobIndex').value;

                const employeeName = document.getElementById('completionActivityEmployeeName').value.trim();

                if (employeeName) {

                    messagesManager.saveLastSelectedAuthor(employeeName); // Save the selected employee

                    messagesManager.updateJobCompletionStatus(messageId, parseInt(jobIndex), true, employeeName);

                    messagesManager.closeEmployeeSelectionModal();

                } else {

                    NotificationManager.show('נא לבחור עובד', 'warning');

                }">

                <div class="modal-body">

                    <input type="hidden" id="completionMessageId">

                    <input type="hidden" id="completionJobIndex">

                   

                    <div class="job-title-display">

                        <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>

                        <span id="completionJobTitle"></span>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label" for="completionActivityEmployeeName">

                            <i class="fas fa-user"></i>

                            שם העובד שביצע את המשימה:

                        </label>

                        <select id="completionActivityEmployeeName"

                                class="form-select"

                                required>

                            <option value="">בחר עובד...</option>

                        </select>

                        <small class="form-help">

                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>

                            נא לבחור את העובד שביצע את המשימה

                        </small>

                    </div>

                </div>

 

                <div class="modal-footer">

                    <div class="form-actions">

                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">

                            <i class="fas fa-check"></i>

                            אשר ביצוע

                        </button>

                        <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="messagesManager.closeEmployeeSelectionModal()">

                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                            ביטול

                        </button>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </form>

        </div>

    </div>

 

    <!-- Employee Completion Modal for Activities -->

    <div id="activityEmployeeCompletionModal" class="skip-reason-modal">

        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">

                <h3 class="modal-title">

                    <i class="fas fa-user-check"></i>

                    סימון משימה כהושלמה

                </h3>

                <button class="close-btn" onclick="activityManager.closeEmployeeCompletionModal()">

                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                </button>

            </div>

            <form id="activityEmployeeCompletionForm" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();

                const taskId = document.getElementById('activityCompletionTaskId').value;

                const employeeName = document.getElementById('activityCompletionEmployeeName').value.trim();

                const executorName = document.getElementById('activityCompletionExecutorName').value.trim();

                if (employeeName) {

                    activityManager.markTaskAsCompleted(taskId, employeeName, executorName);

                    activityManager.closeEmployeeCompletionModal();

                } else {

                    NotificationManager.show('נא להזין שם עובד', 'warning');

                }">

                <div class="modal-body">

                    <input type="hidden" id="activityCompletionTaskId">

                   

                    <div class="task-title-display">

                        <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>

                        <span id="activityCompletionTaskTitle"></span>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label" for="activityCompletionEmployeeName">

                            <i class="fas fa-user"></i>

                            שם העובד שסימן את המשימה:

                        </label>

                        <select id="activityCompletionEmployeeName"

                                class="form-select"

                                required>

                            <option value="">בחר עובד...</option>

                        </select>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label" for="activityCompletionExecutorName">

                            <i class="fas fa-user-cog"></i>

                            שם הגורם שביצע את המשימה:

                        </label>

                        <input type="text" id="activityCompletionExecutorName" class="form-input">

                        <small class="form-help">

                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>

                            השאר ריק אם זהה לעובד שסימן

                        </small>

                    </div>

                </div>

 

                <div class="modal-footer">

                    <div class="form-actions">

                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">

                            <i class="fas fa-check"></i>

                            אשר ביצוע

                        </button>

                        <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="activityManager.closeEmployeeCompletionModal()">

                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                            ביטול

                        </button>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </form>

        </div>

    </div>

 

    <!-- Employee Completion Modal -->

    <div id="employeeCompletionModal" class="skip-reason-modal">

        <div class="modal-content">

            <div class="modal-header">

                <h3 class="modal-title">

                    <i class="fas fa-user-check"></i>

                    סימון משימה כהושלמה

                </h3>

                <button class="close-btn" onclick="dailyTasksManager.closeEmployeeCompletionModal()">

                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                </button>

            </div>

            <form id="employeeCompletionForm" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();

                const taskId = document.getElementById('completionTaskId').value;

                const employeeName = document.getElementById('completionEmployeeName').value.trim();

                if (employeeName) {

                    dailyTasksManager.markTaskAsCompleted(taskId, employeeName);

                    dailyTasksManager.closeEmployeeCompletionModal();

                } else {

                    NotificationManager.show('נא להזין שם עובד', 'warning');

                }">

                <div class="modal-body">

                    <input type="hidden" id="completionTaskId">

                   

                    <div class="task-title-display">

                        <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>

                        <span id="completionTaskTitle"></span>

                    </div>

 

                    <div class="form-group">

                        <label class="form-label" for="completionEmployeeName">

                            <i class="fas fa-user"></i>

                            שם העובד שביצע את המשימה:

                        </label>

                        <select id="completionEmployeeName"

                                class="form-select"

                                required>

                            <option value="">בחר עובד...</option>

                        </select>

                        <small class="form-help">

                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>

                            נא לבחור את העובד שביצע את המשימה

                        </small>

                    </div>

 

                <div class="modal-footer">

                    <div class="form-actions">

                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">

                            <i class="fas fa-check"></i>

                            אשר ביצוע

                        </button>

                        <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="dailyTasksManager.closeEmployeeCompletionModal()">

                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>

                            ביטול

                        </button>

                    </div>

                </div>

            </form>

        </div>

    </div>

 

    <!-- JavaScript Files -->

    <!-- Core Classes -->

    <script src="~/js/flatpickr-helper.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/NotificationManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/SectionManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/ShiftsManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/MessagesManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/ProceduresManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/DailyTasksManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/EmployeeTasksManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/PhoneDirectoryManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/ActivityManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/teamLinksManager.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/NOCPortalApp.js"></script>

    <script src="~/js/SectionDragManager.js"></script>

    <script src="/js/DataCenterManager.js"></script>

    <script src="/js/AlertsManager.js"></script>

    <script src="/js/ChangesManager.js"></script>

 

    <!-- Main Application -->

    <script src="~/js/main.js"></script>

 

</body>

 

</html>
